Package controllers

Class ParkingReservationSummaryController

java.lang.Object
controllers.ParkingReservationSummaryController
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientAware
public class ParkingReservationSummaryController extends Object implements ClientAware
Controller for the reservation summary screen. This screen is shown after a subscriber successfully completes a parking reservation. It displays a confirmation message and shows all reservation details pulled from the Order object.
